B.Ig=new A.cm("pos_earnings_beat","{company} accidentally discovers money behind the couch cushions","{company} reported quarterly earnings 18% above expectations after the CFO found an uncashed cheque in a desk drawer. Guidance raised. Desk drawer to be framed.",5,14,null,!1)
B.Ip=new A.cm("pos_partnership","{company} signs landmark deal with a wizard",'A licensed wizard endorsed {company}\'s blockchain project in a notarised letter sealed with glitter wax. Analysts call it "unverifiable but very bullish."',6,16,null,!1)
B.I6=new A.cm("pos_product_launch","{company} launches product \u2014 customers moderately not confused","{company}'s latest release shipped on time and worked on the first try. Internal Slack was briefly silent with stunned respect. Pre-orders exceeded projections by 40%.",4,12,null,!1)
B.Im=new A.cm("pos_regulatory_approval","Government approves {company} despite not fully reading the application",'Regulators granted {company} approval after a committee member skimmed the executive summary and decided it "sounded fine." Three new markets now open for business.',7,18,null,!1)
B.Iq=new A.cm("pos_buyback",'{company} announces share buyback funded by "found money"','The {company} board approved a $500M repurchase plan funded by what the CFO described in the earnings call as "various jars and at least one shoebox." Investors inexplicably reassured.',3,8,null,!1)
B.Il=new A.cm("pos_analyst_upgrade","Analyst upgrades {company} after reading their Wikipedia page",'A sell-side analyst upgraded {company} to Strong Buy, citing the company\'s "excellent logo" and a hunch described as "professionally developed intuition." Price target raised 35%.',4,10,null,!1)
B.I5=new A.cm("pos_acquisition","{company} acquires startup for three goats and a firm handshake",'{company} completed the acquisition of a private startup for an undisclosed sum that sources describe as "less than you\'d think." Both CEOs described the deal as "very real and definitely happening."',3,9,null,!1)
B.I1=new A.cm("neg_earnings_miss",'{company} misses earnings after CFO confused "revenue" with "vibes"','{company} reported earnings well below expectations. The CFO cited "a fundamental misunderstanding of what numbers mean" and will be retrained on a spreadsheet course starting Monday.',-14,-4,null,!1)
B.I8=new A.cm("neg_lawsuit","{company} sued by a guy who seems really sure about this",'A class of 200,000 plaintiffs filed suit against {company} alleging the company\'s product made their Wi-Fi "feel weird." Legal fees expected to exceed the original product price.',-12,-4,null,!1)
B.Ij=new A.cm("neg_ceo_resign","{company} CEO resigns to pursue career as a competitive eater",'The CEO of {company} stepped down effective immediately. A farewell memo cited "a passion for hot dogs and freedom." The board is reviewing candidates who have not mentioned hot dogs.',-18,-8,null,!1)
B.I2=new A.cm("neg_recall","{company} recalls flagship product after discovering it does the opposite of what it says",'{company} initiated a recall of 1.8 million units. The safety defect was described in the filing as "directionally incorrect functionality." Remediation costs are expected to be considerable.',-15,-6,null,!1)
B.I7=new A.cm("neg_contract_loss","{company} loses contract to competitor who showed up in a nicer van",'A government agency awarded a major contract to a rival after {company}\'s proposal was described as "grammatically brave." The lost revenue represented 12% of annual income.',-11,-5,null,!1)
B.In=new A.cm("neg_analyst_downgrade","Analyst downgrades {company} after personally being annoyed by their app",'A brokerage downgraded {company} to Sell after an analyst experienced three loading spinners in one session and "simply could not let it go." Margin concerns also cited.',-9,-3,null,!1)
B.I4=new A.cm("neg_guidance_cut","{company} cuts guidance after COO accidentally tweets internal memo",'{company} reduced full-year revenue guidance by 8% following what the company calls "a digital communication incident" and what Twitter calls "extremely funny."',-10,-4,null,!1)
B.Ik=new A.cm("sector_pos_tech","Technology sector surges after someone claims AI can now smell money",'A research paper claiming AI can detect financial opportunity via "olfactory market signal modelling" sent technology stocks soaring. Peer review has been requested and not yet performed.',2,7,"Technology",!1)
B.I3=new A.cm("sector_pos_energy","Energy stocks boom as someone unplugs a very important freezer",'A supply shock in global energy markets was traced to a freezer malfunction at a key distribution node. Analysts say the incident was "preventable but extremely profitable for investors."',3,9,"Energy",!1)
B.If=new A.cm("sector_pos_healthcare","Healthcare stocks rally after government discovers people are still sick",'A landmark spending bill expanded coverage for "conditions that are definitely real and not just vibes," boosting revenue projections for all listed healthcare companies.',2,6,"Healthcare",!1)
B.Ic=new A.cm("sector_pos_consumer","Consumer sector surges: people still buying things, experts confirm","A consumer confidence survey hit its highest reading since someone last felt good about things, driving optimism that people will continue to exchange money for objects they want.",1.5,5,"Consumer",!1)
B.Ib=new A.cm("sector_pos_industrial","Industrial sector benefits as government builds a very large thing",'A federal infrastructure bill allocated $400B to domestic manufacturing after a senator reportedly said "let\'s build something big" and nobody disagreed fast enough.',2.5,7,"Industrial",!1)
B.Ih=new A.cm("sector_neg_finance",'Finance sector rattled as central bank raises rates to "make money more expensive, somehow"','The Federal Reserve raised its benchmark rate by 50 basis points and issued a statement that economists described as "technically a sentence." Banking stocks fell on margin pressure fears.',-7,-2,"Finance",!1)
B.Io=new A.cm("sector_neg_tech","Tech sector slumps after regulator learns what an algorithm is",'Regulators launched investigations into tech companies after a committee member Googled "what is software" and became alarmed. Sentiment darkened across the sector pending a follow-up Google.',-6,-2,"Technology",!1)
B.I0=new A.cm("sector_neg_energy",'Energy sector hit after government proposes "the sun should be free"','Proposed energy legislation that one analyst described as "based on vibes and spite" would significantly raise operating costs. Solar companies are most confused.',-8,-3,"Energy",!1)
B.Id=new A.cm("sector_neg_consumer","Consumer sector slumps as people remember they can just not buy things","Consumer spending came in well below forecasts after a widely shared social media post reminded people that saving money is also an option. Discretionary stocks fell sharply.",-5,-2,"Consumer",!1)
B.Ie=new A.cm("sector_neg_entertainment","Streaming sector tanks as viewers discover skill issues with their remote","Subscriber growth decelerated across all platforms after a study found 40% of cancellations stem from users being unable to find anything good and blaming the service personally.",-7,-2.5,"Entertainment",!1)
B.I9=new A.cm("global_crash","GLOBAL SELLOFF: Someone accidentally unplugged the internet",'A facility manager in an undisclosed location tripped over a power cable and caused cascading failures across global markets. The individual has been described as "sheepish but uninjured." All sectors in the red. Circuit breakers triggered.',-14,-8,null,!0)
B.Ia=new A.cm("global_rally","MARKET RALLY: Guy on television seems really confident about everything",'A charismatic financial commentator appeared on three channels simultaneously and said "this is fine, actually" with such conviction that G7 central banks issued a coordinated stimulus package. Risk assets surged across all sectors.',5,10,null,!0)
